Package: sohn
Type: Package
Title: R functions I wished existed, and now do
Version: 0.1.5
Author: Uri Simonsohn [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Uri Simonsohn <urisohn@gmail.com>
Description: Miscellaneous functions for data analysis, visualization, and statistical testing. 
    Provides enhanced versions of common R functions with improved output formatting, 
    additional features, and better integration with data frames. Functions include 
    enhanced plotting (CDFs, densities, frequencies), statistical tests (t-tests with 
    improved output), data manipulation utilities, and formatting helpers.
